cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI 

This paper discusses the design of a machine learning-based classification system for text and images in the online job recruitment domain. The paper focuses on the use of machine learning techniques and algorithms for classification and clustering, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
